<div id="header">Knight Scheduler</div>
<h1>A new scheduling resource for Geneseo Students<img src="/images/beta.png" alt="beta!" id="beta">
</h1>
<div id='landing'>
    <br/>
    <p>Schedule your classes the easy way.</p>
    <p>Browse course listings,<br/>select class sections,<br/>let Knight Scheduler handle the rest.
    
    <div id='begin' class='button_white'>Get Started</div>
    
    <br/>
    
    <div class="wide"><p>The Spring '12 course information is available now! A few courses might be missing, but poke around and let us know what's not there.</p>
    <p>We are currently still testing features, but take a look around and send us feedback at <a href="mailto:err2@geneseo.edu?subject=Knight Scheduler Feedback">err2@geneseo.edu</a> and <a href="mailto:hps1@geneseo.edu?subject=Knight Scheduler Feedback">hps1@geneseo.edu</a>.</p>
    <p>In the mean time, add Knight Scheduler to your bookmarks, share with your friends!</p>
    <p><br/>Thank you!</p>
    <p>Herb Susmann & Elliott Regan</p>
