    </div>
</div>

</div>

    <div id="list">
    
        <div id='list_title'>
            Selected Courses:  <a href='#' class='delete-all'>[clear all]</a>
        </div>
        <div class='list_toggle'>
            <img id='toggle_button'src="images/toggle1.png" alt="toggle button" />
        </div>

        <thread id="course_list"></thread>
        <div id='list_info'>
            <p>This is the list of course sections you have selected. Knight Scheduler will use this list to create a schedule with every course you chose.</p>
            <p>Occasionally, Knight Scheduler may find two courses that overlap, and cannot be placed in the same schedule. Knight Scheduler will create a second schedule with the course that doesn't fit and [eventually] alert you of the overlap.</p>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

